snippet.title: Demonetisation: 25 Deaths Since Government Scrapped Rs 500, Rs 1000 Notes

localized.description:
Demonetisation: 25 deaths have been reported since government scrapped Rs 500, Rs 1000 notes.
There is no end to long queues at banks and ATMs. Peoples are struggling to exchange and deposit currency notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 after Modi government demonetisation decision. In Parliament winter session TMC, Congress, Left, BSP, SP and AAP are attacking Modi government over inconvenience of peoples.
